headline: CHARLOTTE TILBURY REVEALS OFFICIAL BEAUTY LOOK FOR THE DALLAS COWBOYS CHEERLEADERS FOR 2025-26 SEASON, AVAILABLE AT ULTA BEAUTY!
summary: Charlotte Tilbury – the award-winning global luxury makeup, skincare and fragrance brand founded by British entrepreneur and makeup artist to the stars, Charlotte Tilbury MBE – has revealed the official makeup look of the Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders 2025-2026 squad, available now at the nation's largest beauty retailer, Ulta Beauty.
